This is the implementation of STN for the GTSRB problem

For input files:
1. Download the dataset from kaggle or benchmark.ini.rub.de
2. place the test and train folders inside the inputs folder.
3. change and set appropriate paths in all the .py files
  a. signnames.csv has been provided, it has all the 43 class names, used for producing proper output
4. run preprocess.py followed by train.py to start training. finally run test.py to get prediction over some test images
